other_tests.procedure_name: Bilateral Transposition of the Temporal Muscles
other_tests.findings: Surgical procedure performed to transpose the anterior half of the temporal musculofascial flaps to the oral commissures and sling suspension of the lower lip.
Bilateral ectopic ossifications noticed subcutaneously in the zygomatic region.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Ectopic ossifications slowly progressed over time.
